        List getDadaPosicio()
        Deprecated. 
        Gets the value of the DadaPosicio property.

        This accessor method returns a reference to the live list, not a snapshot. Therefore any modification you make to the returned list will be present inside the JAXB object. This is why there is not a set method for the DadaPosicio property.

            getDadaPosicio().add(newItem);
